Module 1: Project Planning
Chapter 2: Restaurant Website Architecture
Project Name

AI Restaurant Ordering Website Using Flask + Gemini + Voiceflow + Replit

1. What is Website Architecture?

Website Architecture is the overall structure and organization of a website.

It defines:

How pages are connected
How users navigate
Where information is stored
How the AI chatbot communicates with the backend

A well-designed architecture makes the website easy to use, easy to maintain, and scalable.

2. Why Do We Need Website Architecture?

Imagine a restaurant website with no structure.

Problems:

Customers cannot find the menu.
Contact details are difficult to locate.
Ordering process becomes confusing.
AI chatbot has no proper integration.

A planned architecture ensures a smooth user experience.

